strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_TWINSBLESSING_KEYWOR: <style=cKeywordName><color=#00BDFF>Atuykarounkami's Blessings</color></style><style=cSub>On impact, create a <style=cIsDamage>tidal blast</style> on nearby surface that deals <style=cIsDamage>???% damage</style>
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_TWINSSHOCK_KEYWORD: <style=cKeywordName><color=#000FFF>Shocking</color></style><style=cSub>Interrupts enemies and stuns them. The stun is removed if the target takes more than <style=cIsHealth>10%</style> of their maximum health in damage.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_TWINSRAYCAST_KEYWORD: <style=cKeywordName><style=cIsDamage>Tiriryarai</style></style><style=cSub>Skill activates at your <style=cIsUtility>crosshair's location</style> with <style=cIsUtility>no travel time</style>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_TWINSWIND_KEYWORD: <style=cKeywordName><color=#0b9c2d>Wind God's Perfect Defense</color></style><style=cSub>Block most attacks while channeling.</style>
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_PASSIVE_NAME: Ever Turning, Ever Swaying, Ever Drifting
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_PASSIVE_DESCRIPTION: Ururuu and Saraana have independent loadouts and <style=cIsUtility>switch turns</style> upon reaching maximum <color=#EDA717>Zeal</color>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_PRIMARY0_DESCRIPTION: Fire a <color=#4d108f>shadow sphere</color> for <style=cIsDamage>290% damage</style> that <style=cIsDamage>explodes</style> on impact. Hold up to 4.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_PRIMARY1_DESCRIPTION: Repeatedly fire tracking <color=#4d108f>energy bolts</color> for <style=cIsDamage>???% damage</style>. Continous fire will charge a <color=#4d108f>shadow sphere</color> that can be released for <style=cIsDamage>600% damage</style>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_PRIMARY2_DESCRIPTION: <style=cIsDamage>Tiriryarai</style>. Hold to sow <color=#4d108f>seeds of darkness</color>. Release to <color=#4d108f>harvest</color> for <style=cIsDamage>???% damage</style> plus an additional <style=cIsDamage>???% damage</style> per <color=#4d108f>seed</color>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_SECONDARY1_DESCRIPTI: <style=cIsDamage>Stunning</style>. Fire a boulder for <style=cIsDamage>???% damage</style> that splinters into smaller debris for <style=cIsDamage>200% damage</style> each.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_SECONDARY0_DESCRIPTI: <style=cIsDamage>Ignite</style>. Conjure a slow-moving molten ball that <style=cIsDamage>burns</style> nearby enemies for <style=cIsDamage>150%-250% damage</style>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_SECONDARY3_DESCRIPTI: <style=cIsUtility>Freezing</style>. Summon a pillar of ice to periodically damage nearby enemies for <style=cIsDamage>???% damage</style>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_SECONDARY2_DESCRIPTI: <color=#0b9c2d>Wind God's Perfect Defense</color>. Channel the <style=cIsUtility>fortune of the winds</style> for <style=cIsUtility>2s</style>. Fully channel to <style=cIsUtility>decrease all your cooldowns</style> by <style=cIsUtility>2s</style> or <style=cIsDamage>attack</style> to cancel <style=cIsUtility>early</style> and fire a <style=cIsDamage>blade of wind</style>. The blade slices enemies for <style=cIsDamage>???% damage</style> and <style=cIsDamage>returns</style> to you.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_UTILITY0_DESCRIPTION: <style=cIsDamage>Tiriryarai</style>. Strike an enemy with lightning for <style=cIsDamage>1000% damage</style> and create <style=cIsDamage>3</style> aftershocks that seek enemies for <style=cIsDamage>500% damage</style>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_UTILITY1_DESCRIPTION: Fire a series of water bolts that deal <style=cIsDamage>250% damage</style> each. The number of bolts fired increases with attack speed. <style=cIsDamage>Critical Strikes</style> become <color=#00BDFF>Atuykarounkami's Blessings</color>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_UTILITY2_DESCRIPTION: <style=cIsDamage>Tiriryarai</style>. Call for the Mirage Blade's assistance. His afterimages strike enemies for <style=cIsDamage>???% damage</style> repeatedly.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_UTILITY3_DESCRIPTION: Conjure a <style=cIsUtility>miasma</style> over the targeted area. Enemies that die inside the miasma have their <style=cIsUtility>souls captured</style> temporarily.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_SPECIAL0_DESCRIPTION: Unleash a <color=#4d108f>roar of darkness</color> for <style=cIsDamage>9800%</style> total <style=cIsDamage>damage</style>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_SPECIAL1_DESCRIPTION: Mark an area to be sealed after <style=cIsUtility>2.5s</style>. Once primed, the seal detonates, dealing <style=cIsDamage>650% damage</style>. Enemies below <style=cIsHealth>20% health are executed.</style>
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_EXTRA1_DESCRIPTION: <style=cIsUtility>Disappear</style> into the aether and become <style=cIsUtility>invulnerable</style> for a short time.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_EXTRA2_DESCRIPTION: <style=cIsDamage>Stunning</style>. Deal <style=cIsDamage>175% damage</style>, briefly <style=cIsUtility>disappear</style>, and then <style=cIsUtility>reappear</style> in a nearby location.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_EXTRA4_DESCRIPTION: Call Mothmoth to the battlefield. He grants <style=cIsHealth>lifesteal</style> to nearby allies.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_EXTRA3_DESCRIPTION: <style=cIsUtility>Push</style> away enemies and conjure an <style=cIsUtility>impenetrable barrier</style> that is <style=cIsHealth>impassable from the outside</style>.
